title: MFTE 1-Bed Unit with AC. 75% AMI
posting_body: ["Please review all MFTE information on the city's website before contacting us!", 'The Cove is an award winning, LEED Platinum community right in the heart of Capitol Hill.', 'Each of our pet-friendly homes comes equipped with programmable A/C units; full-size, front-load washers and dryers; as well as spacious kitchens with energy efficient stainless steel appliances including full- and XL-sized fridges/freezers and full-sized dishwashers.', 'Lofty ceilings open up your living space allowing sunlight to stream in through over-sized floor-to-ceiling windows.', 'The Cove’s excellent location makes it easy to navigate the city in any direction.', 'Both downtown Seattle and Capitol Hill’s light rail station are only 10 minute walks, and Microsoft’s Connector Bus stop is only a block away.', 'Proximity to major grocery stores including Whole Foods, QFC, and Amazon’s novel Amazon Go Grocery make car-free living easy!', 'BUILDING AMENITIES', '1GB/sec High-Speed Internet', 'Fitness Center', 'Gated Parking Garage', 'PET POLICY', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed with some breed restrictions', 'Pet deposits start at $250.00', 'Pet rent: $35.00/cat, $45.00/dog', 'Application Fee: $55/adult', 'Security Deposits start at: $750', 'Good credit required', 'Income must be at least 3 times the rental rate', 'Minimum Lease: 10 Months', 'Included Utilities: None', 'Resident pays for electric, water, sewer, trash.']
